\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1009002 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10504500\charrsid12200121 
Five of us living. That's right. There were three brothers and - and two sisters. The sister were youngest and our George older, he were the oldest. But Joe - there were Joseph, George and Thomas in boys. And me sister called Elizabeth. }{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6165473\charrsid12200121 Called}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10504500\charrsid12200121  me Alice Mary after me mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3230341 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10504500\charrsid12200121 It's Elizabeth who's still alive?
