\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3230341 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10504500\charrsid12200121 How much is Tom older than you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1009002 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10504500\charrsid12200121 That's the youngest. He's they youngest one, yes. About two and }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3884354\charrsid12200121 half}{
