s it is. Doctor says he can't get better, so Mrs Marriot asked me to send for you as the only one turned - being so far - I was seven mile away. And - she sent word back to say would I go and - would I - would me mother go and send for us. So I come back.
 
And - I was sat - sat there and look at him 'til he put his head back like that. And he - he eventually wanted a smoke. So I got hold of his pipe and I lit his pipe for him but he couldn't puff it, it - I put it in - right to his lips, he just went - thre
e times. And he's kicked - kicked the bath nearly over, he'd gone in me arms. Couldn't shift behind back of chair a little bit. And it's all over. Well I seen right when he was in his coffin. Yes.
