 were born and me boy were born, and he's about - me eldest - eldest what's living, she's about fifty-four. And there's our Nellie she's - fifty-two. And then there's our Alice comes in between. 'Cos there's only fourteen months in them two. You'll know h
ow old Alice is then won't you? Well I'd them - I had them four and then I had the others - yes.
