Our Alice - the fourth oldest, she was two year and a half when her dad come home from soldiering. That's Alice, that's the - youngest in the four }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6165473\charrsid12200121 oldest}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
