\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3230341 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10504500\charrsid12200121 What was the paper you used to get, do you remember?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1009002 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10504500\charrsid12200121 The Star we used to call it, Star were it then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3230341 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10504500\charrsid12200121 Was it the Rotherham Star?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1009002 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10504500\charrsid12200121 Yes. Star.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3230341 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10504500\charrsid12200121 That was an evening paper was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1009002 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10504500\charrsid12200121 Yes, Star at night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3230341 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10504500\charrsid12200121 What would you get on a Sunday, can you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1009002 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10504500\charrsid12200121 News of the World. Used to have News of the World, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3230341 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10504500\charrsid12200121 Did you ever get any magazines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1009002 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10504500\charrsid12200121 No.
