\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1009002 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10504500\charrsid12200121 Yes, our Thomas, yes.
