Well - she partly did. But I couldn't get a house then, we couldn't get a house for love nor money. But I did get a little house, and then he went - I 
had our - had two babies - no, I had one. I had our Annie, well he went soldiering then. And then no - I had two, I had our - no, I had Harold in me mother's - had both of them at me mother's.
\par 
