Well - no, I - I had milk, I had plenty of milk, I don't know where it used to come from sometimes. I don't. I was all right, I were fifteen stone two. Oh aye, yes, I've a photo - I've a photo of me when - took outside with me young - me youngest l
ad like what's living, this boy who's living. I've always been - a big - fine la-s you know. Have to work you know, go to work. Oh aye.
