ess is all right, she's going on grand. He said well it is - to tell you the truth Mrs Burton, she said, I thought I'd seen the blind - me mother told me this after, she said, a blind down for Alice, she was so poorly. So an old lady in - in the lane - an
d
 - and she were a nice old neighbour in - me mother's - talk a bit together, right - and - she told her. She said, Mrs Burton, said, I'll tell you want to do with Alice. She said, you get a big jug of boiling hot water - and put a half an ounce of Friar's
 
Balsam in it, and it all goes like coddly on top you know, and she said, let her breathe - her bronchitis is for - and she said let her breathe over it, put a blanket over her head. And let her breathe through - onto jug like, inhale it. Mm. So I did do. 
A
nd I did it three times that day. Said next morning I could - I could sup the same day. So anyway - you feeling better Alice? Oh I said, I do mother, I said, I feel a lot better with that stuff. She said, well keep on while it moves then. So when Doctor R
i
ddle come down the next day to see me and he says, well, by gum Mrs - Burton, he says, there's big alterations here. He said, what have you been doing? Well it's a simple thing doctor, I don't know whether you've heard about it or not. But says there was 
an old lady says - lives at - up the - lane here, she says, she told me, she asked me how she was and I told her, and she says - what I}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2714250\charrsid12200121  do}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10504500\charrsid12200121  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2714250\charrsid12200121 w}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10504500\charrsid12200121 
hat she - he telled her like. And she said I told her it was the only thing as could get her round. So I says - she t
ook a - I got a jug, this here what I got in, I said, and inhale it, inhale it and he said, now how often did you do that? I said, about three times. So he says, by gum, he says, I've never heard such a thing. And I've been a doctor all these years, he'll
 be dead and buried now, he says - he said, I've never known a simple thing like that. And he'd never heard of it. Well anyway he said, he said well you've been a miracle to your daughter. She got me round, me mother. She got us both round. Mm.
