\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1009002 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10504500\charrsid12200121 Well - if she didn't cry nor nothing like that, as long as nothing wrong with her - I'd try - I'd just give her a - drop when I felt f
it to give her a drop, see if she did take it. But - they've all been right - right good at breast. You know. Oh never had no trouble with nothing like that, no, not a bit of trouble. Only our Nellie I tell you, she were born - pregnant with our Nellie sh
e were born - with a cracked palate. That was through me with me throat you know. 'Cos I was going to tell you.
