 and he says - he says, I know - I think I know this little face. He says, I've seen you before. So she looked at him, shy at him you know. He said aren't - aren't you called Mrs - Ellen Scroop? I said yes. He said, I'm sure I've seen her, I said you did,
 probably did. I said, she were only three days old. YES? THE same baby. And is this - Ellen? I said, yes. Well he says, she has a suc - successful operation, and she'll talk as plain as you once she starts talking.
