rs Scroop. I says, oh I says - my little Billy, I said, gone and had his fingers, his mother'll tell you. She says - and he were crying. Oh, I says, he's cried doctor. Oh, crying'll not hurt him. Said, it'll do him good to cry. Do you know, I were heartbr
