\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1009002 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10504500\charrsid12200121 Oh he wouldn't - no, he never touched the children, never - tell you neither of us, nobody ever touched our children. No.
